Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在屋顶太热了没法练习可是鸣和多美姐说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,说「那么就在游泳池练习吧」而很开心地接受了的也是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快啦  大家都在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,夜弥  知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,开始练习吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要比较啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H492C15&\fs48\b1\frz286.4\move(217.5,207,198,160.5,30,500)}抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再从头来一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  果然还是要队形整齐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,准备～
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== A PART ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500,1050)}果然还是好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:42.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500,970)}虽然比在屋顶练习要好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要稍微休息一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真智学姐在关心我们!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不能关心的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,夜弥真是的  回敬!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真敢做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那就跳进去呗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸣也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真智也进来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜也来游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是旱鸭子来着的!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fn方正卡通_GBK\bord2\pos(1026,300)}{\ko25\c&H7FF5F1&\2a&HFF&\3c&H2534A9&&}救　{\ko25}援　{\ko25}中　{\ko20}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fn方正卡通_GBK\bord10\1a&HFF&\pos(1026,300)}{\ko25\c&H7FF5F1&\2a&HFF&\3c&H53A0EA&}救　{\ko25}援　{\ko25}中　{\ko20}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜  没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还好  没啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还好来看看你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是要注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,老师很擅长游泳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜  抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.61,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我运动神经好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:00.81,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8}再夸夸我也没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.02,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8}少得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,arrive…到达…成田?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谁发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H46174D&\b1\pos(766.5,352.5)}哈娜的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,最近从美国到了这边准备住在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H46174D&\b1\pos(766.5,352.5)}哈娜的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H46174D&\b1\pos(766.5,352.5)}哈娜的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H46174D&\b1\pos(766.5,352.5)}哈娜的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是来见你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么情绪那么低落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能和妈妈一起住虽然很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,信息里还写了要是成绩不好就埋了你什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,埋…埋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,成绩怎么样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,理科和数学虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,语文和英语就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是英语…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\pos(348,328.5)\b1}【英语测验】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\pos(402,450)\b1}1　 请把下列日文翻译成英文。
