Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\fs54\pos(1387.5,267)}②  Katashi reads books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\fs54\pos(526.5,657)\clip(m 510 606 b 570 648 570 660 600 711 l 1182 504 1116 441)}③  They were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\fs54\pos(1426.5,387)}④  She played the piano yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\fs54\pos(562.5,777)\alpha&HFF&\clip()}⑤  {\fad(400,150)\alpha&H00&}She was playing the piano yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\fs54\pos(1467,510)}⑥  He listens to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.77,TEST,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(400,50)\fs54\pos(594,894)\clip(m 630 843 b 633 876 624 918 615 942 l 1338 714 1338 606)}⑦  Did he listen to music at that time?
