Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H5F314C&\fs54\frz262.5\move(1665,358.5,1686,355.5,21,521)}秃头海怪\N挺能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H5F314C&\fs54\frz262.5\move(1683,349.5,1654.5,309,23,190)}秃头海怪\N挺能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正卡通_GBK\bord0\be1\shad0\c&H5F314C&\fs54\frz262.5\move(1653,306,1672.5,306,22,480)}秃头海怪\N挺能干嘛
