Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能见到面就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  秃头海怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她还没登机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,夜弥同学  多美同学还有真智同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是来送行而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想在最后说一声你这个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这点小事你如实地说出来就好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜  夜来舞我们会连你的份一起跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后跳舞的时候我们大家永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,总之  歌完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.27,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8}干脆地  利落地  就像花那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:47.32,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8}风姿绰约地  竞相开放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,果然没有她的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们开始练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,鸣?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和哈娜说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,即使哈娜不在了  我们也要好好地跳夜来舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,距离比赛还有一周的时间了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哈娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是带给我梦想和一段美好的相识的宝物
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== YOKOKU ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然分别了但我们心意依然相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧  哈娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  Ha·Na·Ya·MA·Ta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起来  HaNaYaMaTa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没能同步
